<h2>Astro</h2>
<h3>Amateur astronomical computations</h3>
<p>Amateur astronomical computations: rise and set times and azimuths, coordinates, distances, angular sizes and other parameters of the Sun, the Moon, planets and stars.</p>
<p>Web UI: <a href="../astro.html">Astro UI</a>.</p>
<p>Related tags: <a href="../tag/astro.html">astro</a></p>
<p>Source code: <a href="https://github.com/aligusnet/astro">github</a></p>
